headline: Paychex Completes Acquisition of Paycor
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., April 14, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) ("Paychex"), an industry-leading human capital management (HCM) company, today announced the successful completion of its acquisition of Paycor HCM, Inc. (Nasdaq: PYCR) ("Paycor"), a leading provider of HCM, payroll and talent software.
